## 5. Definition of Done

- 4 atomic commits in `main` (one per component, Layer 3 SERIAL pattern).
- Frontend typecheck: 0 errors (`pnpm exec tsc -p tsconfig.app.json --noEmit`).
- All component `.spec.ts` files updated and passing.
- `pnpm test` (frontend unit tests): all green.
- No new `box-shadow`, `rounded-md/lg/3xl`, `bg-white` introduced.
- All hairline borders use `var(--color-rule)` (warm, not pure black).
- All form labels migrated from `variant="required"` to `variant="eyebrow" [required]="true"`.
- Operational pages (login, materials, organizations, dictionaries, etc.) compile and render correctly with new defaults.
- Browser-use visual verify on `/materials`, `/organizations`, `/dictionaries` (Light + Dark) — **NOTE**: blocked by authGuard, see TZ-93 known limitation. Typecheck is the primary verification gate until TZ-93.1/TZ-95 resolves the auth wall.

