## 6. What is NOT in this TZ (explicit deferrals)

- ❌ **Auth wall resolution — TZ-92b (resolved 2026-07-12)** — investigation found `/kit/*` is ALREADY public (no canMatch). The actual browser-use blocker was misdiagnosed; visual verify to be attempted during TZ-94/TZ-95 implementation via `start.mjs` (handles dev proxy correctly). No route changes needed; TZ-92b adds JSDoc + route test for defensive contract pinning. See `tasks/TZ-92b.md`.
- ❌ **TZ-95 (showcase + docs)** — update `/kit/*` pages + `docs/paper-and-ink.md` + `docs/add-new-page.md`. Phase 3 of the refinement.
- ❌ **Other components** (PiCard, PiDialog, PiInput, etc.) — TZ-94 focuses on the 4 components the user explicitly requested. Other components can adopt TZ-93 utilities in future TZs.
- ❌ **New component variants** — no new PiBadge variants, no new PiLabel variants. Just refactoring existing ones.
- ❌ **Theme overrides** — no live OKLCH theme editor updates for the new patterns. Theme editor already covers `--color-rule`, `--font-mono`, etc.

