## 8. Acceptance Examples

### Before/After: PiBadge

```html
<!-- BEFORE: solid fills -->
<app-pi-badge variant="default">ACTIVE</app-pi-badge>
<!-- Renders: <span class="... bg-sunrise-warm text-paper">ACTIVE</span> -->

<!-- AFTER: hairline border + transparent bg -->
<app-pi-badge variant="default">ACTIVE</app-pi-badge>
<!-- Renders: <span class="... bg-transparent hairline border-sunrise-warm text-sunrise-warm">ACTIVE</span> -->
```

### Before/After: PiEmptyState

```html
<!-- BEFORE: simple text in <td> -->
<tr>
  <td colspan="5" class="py-12 px-4 text-center text-muted-foreground">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
      <span class="eyebrow text-sunrise-warm">00</span>
      <span class="text-sm">Нет материалов для отображения.</span>
    </div>
  </td>
</tr>

<!-- AFTER: centered dropzone panel (pi-corner-marks removed in TZ-93.1) -->
<tr>
  <td colspan="5" class="py-12 px-4 text-center text-muted-foreground">
    <div class="max-w-sm mx-auto p-6 pi-dashed-panel
                flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
      <span class="eyebrow text-sunrise-warm">00</span>
      <span class="text-sm">Нет материалов для отображения.</span>
    </div>
  </td>
</tr>
```

### Before/After: PiLabel / PiFormField

```html
<!-- BEFORE: variant="required" mixes typography + state -->
<app-pi-form-field label="Email" [required]="true" htmlFor="email">
  <app-pi-input id="email" type="email" />
</app-pi-form-field>

<!-- AFTER: variant="eyebrow" + standalone required input -->
<app-pi-form-field label="Email" [required]="true" htmlFor="email">
  <app-pi-input id="email" type="email" />
</app-pi-form-field>
<!-- Label renders: <label class="eyebrow">Email <span>*</span></label> -->
```

